================================================================================
 LOVE ME INTERNATIONAL — DEVELOPER LOG
================================================================================

Purpose
-------
A running journal of actual development work on this Flutter app. Every time a
real change is made (dependencies added, a feature/screen built, a bug fixed,
config changed, a spec conflict resolved), append a dated entry below.

This file records what was DONE, not what is planned. Plans live in README.md
and the specs under `app doctumant/`.

Entry format
------------
[YYYY-MM-DD] <Phase / area>
  - What changed (files touched, packages added)
  - Why
  - Result / verification (build ran? tests? manual check?)
  - Open items / follow-ups

